LAGOS – Lagos State chapter of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) has hailed the emergence of former Vice President Atiku Abubakar as the presidential flag bearer of the party in 2023, stressing that he is the best person that can lead the party to victory in the polls. The party noted in a congratulatory message on Wednesday that the emergence of Alhaji Atiku Abubakar as the presidential flag bearer of the PDP, has been described as a true democrat taking over governance, as the 2023 election would be a landslide victory for the party. The PDP, Lagos State chapter, made the declaration in a congratulatory message to Atiku, a former Vice President, who was elected as the party’s presidential candidate at last Saturday’s primaries. -Advertisement- According to Lagos PDP, Atiku is “the brightest of stars in Nigeria today when it comes to true democracy.” The congratulatory message which was signed by the Lagos state State Publicity Secretary of the party,  Hakeem Amode, stated, “Alhaji Atiku Abubakar’s emergence as our party’s presidential candidate has put a seal on our readiness to take back power at the centre.”